author: wcax.com
title: Nighttime work planned on I-93 in Concord
text:
CONCORD, N.H. (AP) - Nighttime drainage work on Interstate 93 in Concord is resulting in some lane closures between Exits 12 and 13.
The work in the median area between the exits starts after 7 p.m. Monday and is scheduled for each night through Thursday.
Northbound and southbound lane closures will be in place.
